Given Directions:
    Java program to find the sum of positive numbers.
    
Directions found by the students after contacting teacher:
    Sum user inputed numbers until user enters a negative - 
    print sum. 
    
Directions found after my inQuery: 
    Get input from user until they stop: set stop condition as you see fit. - 
        Only sum up positive numbers, and if user enters a negative number, - 
        it shouldn't be summed.
